Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.90,0:00:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有忘記帶的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.09,0:00:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果遇到困難
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要立刻去找老師喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.08,0:00:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後不要繞去其他地方喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.06,0:00:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我出門了 迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.91,0:00:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼斯 莉塔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.11,0:00:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心 拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.89,0:00:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記叫她不要跟著陌生人走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.27,0:00:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧他能每天早上一直重覆這些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從拉提娜開始去學校上課
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.03,0:00:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明也都過好一段時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(眼眸的深處照映著我的模樣)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(你的笑容令我感到些許耀眼)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(在四目相對的瞬間)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.81,0:01:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(便已感受到 I feel it)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(如空中出現的)\N((那片天空的))
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.03,0:01:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(那道彩虹一樣)\N((彩虹一般))
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(閃耀著七色光輝)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.92,0:01:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(與你共度的時光)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(使我的內心雀躍不已)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.92,0:01:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(I'm with you)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(不論是笑容 又或是傷悲)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(我願分享我的一切)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.14,0:01:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(只要你能對我微笑)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.48,0:01:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(哪怕猛烈強風 亦或漫長黑夜)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:01:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(只要你陪伴在我身邊 僅僅如此)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.78,0:02:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(就令我感覺能再踏出下一步)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(小小女孩 被雪深深感動)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.19,0:02:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家裡幫忙不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是送東西比較好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎 馬賽爾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.07,0:02:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來好像很傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說他爸爸的誕生月快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想該送他甚麼禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要先看有多少預算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以先考慮自己買得起的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今年送我爸爸手套當禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花紋還是我刺的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要馬賽爾的心意能傳達出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管送甚麼我想他都會開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預算…心意…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而覺得越來越難決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生甚麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊 那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.25,0:03:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜有事想拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作不要太勉強自己喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.65,0:03:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家路上請小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在天黑後也越來越冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.46,0:03:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘也要小心別感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 再找間店喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜連接待客人都很完美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說不定天生就很有才能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是料理或打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都只教過拉提娜一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的學習速度真的很快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她之前甚麼都不會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反而覺得不可思議呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:03:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是刀子的握法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或擰抹布的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我從頭教她的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說她不會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說是不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是甚麼事都沒人教她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就是處在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼都不必做的環境中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說拉提娜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜在來這裡之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有像我跟肯尼斯教你學東西這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有其他人教你各式各樣的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜以前沒有做決定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼東西沒有做決定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜也不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢 莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜甚麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子一旦這樣就不會說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用說沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊 迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在放學之後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以去克蘿伊家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天難得能趕在天黑前回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜一定會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜 我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜還沒有回來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說甚麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是有先回來一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後馬上就去克蘿伊家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來她最近每天都這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和朋友感情這麼好是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起拉提娜帶著笑容說"歡迎回來"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來滋潤我的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並為此全力衝刺跑回來的我的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定…大概…重要多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是她先知道你會這麼早回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜應該就不會出門了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用這樣安慰我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是在安慰你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看待會就讓拉提娜嚇一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:06:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她的笑容提升三倍威力好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是隨便想想的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對象是克蘿伊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就算想吃醋也沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得克蘿伊家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是做裁縫的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且技術精良 廣受好評呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對對 縫得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜東西學得真快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要和拉提娜在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克蘿伊也會提起幹勁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她雖然素質不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她一下就厭倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不肯好好練習
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該謝謝你的人是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 這邊再來一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追加兩份魚排
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒看過生意像今天這麼好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:06:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以請你說"比平常還好"嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烘烤雞準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 把那個拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們未免也太愛使喚拉提娜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做甚麼把話說得這麼難聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是有付錢給她的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜是我們店裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式僱用的店員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她還是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不會讓她在深夜工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們有付恰當的金額給她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒看過拉提娜身上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那種多餘的錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她大概是存起來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾那小子是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他一副要死不活的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾先生 今天晚上很冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照這樣子看來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚可能會下雪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道甚麼是雪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在繪本上有看過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是白白的軟綿綿的東西對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒看到有長角啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是避免被發現所以折斷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有靠山的異族小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以賣到一個好價錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太大聲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢我放這
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看我也該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能下雪就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在回家路上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託天空下雪的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在樓上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:08:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要今天交給她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜竟然瞞著我工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是不是有想要甚麼東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.89,0:09:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今只要是拉提娜想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都會買一大堆給她的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說拉提娜是在對我客氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這也沒甚麼好責怪她的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼向拉提娜問這件事才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有甚麼想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要客氣你儘管說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說你根本沒必要跟我客氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然晚了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是迪爾的誕生月禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是拉提娜自己做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要送迪爾先生禮物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜跟馬賽爾一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:10:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道該送甚麼禮物比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是最近流行的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是配有雙頭蛇的裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如要送私人用品的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印有飛龍的背心好像也很受歡迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希爾維亞在這方面很了解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是真的很懂這些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我家附近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多對這些事很講究的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親手做禮物怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親手做?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才會去克蘿伊家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,線跟布的材料也都是拉提娜買的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想用自己賺的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買做禮物的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾 你願意收下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是比任何金銀財寶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都還要棒的寶物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.99,0:10:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是全世界最幸福的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是開始傻笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他終於發瘋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜想要錢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.81,0:11:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是拉提娜想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾都會買很多很多回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還送了好多好多的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但拉提娜都沒辦法回報他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連誕生月也都沒辦法送他禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你想要送迪爾禮物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜也想送迪爾禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞞著迪爾偷偷準備是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道迪爾會不會又驚又喜的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話我會很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不只是幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是用工作的認真態度努力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就可以付你工錢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是拉提娜還是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:11:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大多數的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是從門徒開始做起的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微提早一點沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當門徒就可以工作了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾他其實自豪得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜你的成績很好不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要當門徒是也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但努力讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入高等學校也是一種選擇喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然讀書也很快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但等我長大以後如果想讀書了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候多的是時間可以讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為拉提娜是魔人族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 你說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在拉提娜想跟肯尼斯學很多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能像肯尼斯一樣做出美味的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拉提娜的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也得好好加油才行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼斯也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能一直當拉提娜的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣拉提娜要追上去會很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我家拉提娜為了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就"只"為了我一個人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這刺繡簡直是職業水準啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好厲害啊 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堆雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堆好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白茫茫的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔 快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道路跟屋頂都變得比剛才還要白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她從醒來後就一直那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來她今天也無心工作了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.42,0:13:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說是第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但沒想到拉提娜會這麼興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冰喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾你看 是雪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去外面看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用跑的 會滑倒的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冰喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜還想在外面玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再繼續留在外面拉提娜會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡水已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:14:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去洗個澡暖暖身子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪要是積得再厚一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她大概會更開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟這一帶很少會下雪嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我故鄉那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪只會讓人感到鬱悶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,視狀況而定甚至會攸關人命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看拉提娜興奮成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺還挺新鮮的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還有一點殘雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面絕對不能用跑的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪會從屋頂掉下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也不能走在路邊喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾工作也要加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.19,0:15:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會趕快把魔獸給殺光盡早回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜會等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶神惡煞的台詞跟畫面的落差
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.37,0:15:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而醞釀出一股韻味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完全是這裡的招牌景象了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾先生 請用熱茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這種日子喝熱茶是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜倒是希望能再冷一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就會下更多的雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到雪覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.70,0:16:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊 然後啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和迪爾一起去外面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這陣暴風雪是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是帶拉提娜一起過來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.76,0:16:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會有甚麼樣的反應呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和小姑娘聊天感覺真愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和吉爾先生一起聊雪的話題覺得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:16:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝招待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是承蒙惠顧了 吉爾維斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地上很滑 走路時要小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吉爾維斯特忘記拿的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用特地追上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很快就會來店裡 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的東西忘記拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是掉在店裡面的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你特地追過來拿給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人回得去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:17:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜回得去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一直線而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以再用跑的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾先生再見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是冒險者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有點事想問小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.06,0:18:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請去問衛兵先生或憲兵先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人不是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓她逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是上等貨色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:18:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓她留下大傷口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可以使用攻擊魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要使用的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在你覺得不使用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會有危險的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見過你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…甚麼都沒做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是想向那孩子問路罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說的話就只有這些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在那裡做甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是吉爾維斯特嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我們庫羅茲的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憲兵副隊長殿下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子一臉死板的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這兩個人帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們甚麼都還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們說"還沒"是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的我待會再慢慢聽你們說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近這陣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有買賣異族的黑市份子出沒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:21:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類城市少見的魔人族小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別容易被他們盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是拉提娜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.73,0:21:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我常常聽說你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我女兒希爾維亞口中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是希爾維亞的爸爸?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下次也繞去虎貓亭坐坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是別了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣那群大老粗會連酒都喝不下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒覺得我還比你好一點就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要去迎接拉提娜的三倍笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾維斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼吉爾維斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.81,0:21:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會和我家的拉提娜在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.63,0:21:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她送我拿忘記帶走的東西過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.18,0:21:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(每過一秒 對你的喜歡就增加一點)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.97,0:22:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(當你磨蹭我的臉龐)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.96,0:22:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(一切都變得不再重要)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.76,0:22:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(發生在世上的紛爭 都敵不過這個瞬間)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(如果可以真希望明天或者後天)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.60,0:22:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(都因為溺愛中毒丟下工作不管)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.53,0:22:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(已經超乎保護過度 愛操心的毛病)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(使得我變得異常堅強)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.94,0:22:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(我已下定決心要守護你)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.56,0:23:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(只要是為了你的笑容)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(我甚至能與正義為敵)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(This is 勇者 but 殘念!?)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(對你深深著迷)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.79,0:23:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(甜甜蜜蜜或是卿卿我我)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(都是傻爸爸的末期症狀)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.33,0:23:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(只要有你在)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.50,0:23:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(就算當個殘念勇者也無所謂)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.71,0:23:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(所以請你永遠陪伴在我身邊)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(到連冒險也無法繼續的地步)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(This is 勇者 but 殘念)